Steps:
1) we will make the adjacency list
2) After that we will declare an time array (vector) with a value of INT_MAX (same as we declare a distance[n] array in dijsktra algorithm) and a vector ways which will store the number of ways to reach a particular node.
3) Then just apply the direct dijsktra alogrithm and while traversing in adjList[node] we will store the shortest time and the number to ways to the same node with the same shortest distance and with the same shortest time possible.


